### Import NBA 2025 Data - Complete Process
### Run these in sequence to import your CSE placement data

### Step 1: Login as Admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@piemr.edu.in",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Step 2: Preview the Excel file structure
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/validate/preview-nba2025
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Step 3: Import NBA 2025 data (46 CSE students)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/data/process-nba2025
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Step 4: Verify the import - Check all alumni
GET http://localhost:8080/api/alumni?page=0&size=50
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Step 5: Check CSE 2022 batch specifically
GET http://localhost:8080/api/alumni/batch/2022/CSE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Step 6: Get batch statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/batches/2022/CSE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Step 7: Test search functionality
GET http://localhost:8080/api/alumni/search?q=Abhinay
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Step 8: Check company-wise alumni (e.g., Zehntech)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/alumni/company/Zehntech
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Step 9: Get all batches for the website
GET http://localhost:8080/api/batches
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Step 10: Get placement trends for analytics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/batches/trends
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
